# This program calculates uniformly distributed
# pseudo random numbers U[i] in the range 0 <= U[i] <= 1
#
# U[i] = Fractional part of (PI + U[i-1])^5
#
# The user has to specify the starting value U[0] such that
# 0 <= U[0] <= 1
#
